column5: We will be repowering the rescue boat I have potentially for sale 3 volvo marinized 4.3 chevy motors 1 is 500 or so hour rail injected the other 2 are throttle body injected high hours also 3 sx drives 2 of them have 1 season on them and the other is rebuilt with props and spare props(stainless)going with this is all parts in stores and anything else we cannot carry foward I will not attach a price yet as this is just a feeler to see if anyone on this site has a use this will not be seperated and sold all as is I figured i will let first choice go to this site before it goes else where if interested pm me  Peter   Guess I better add this price will be over 10k this will be the whole drive line hull rings and all
